race.comment: Can the winning streak continue? There is a good chance it can as GURU WARRIOR (3) finds the right race to continue his rise through the ranks. He's been winning comfortably while still doing a bit wrong. The step to 2250m looks suitable and unless he regresses, there doesn't appear to be anything that will trouble him too much. Think he can win again and put a margin on them again. TALISAY (8) has ability but she was almost 4L off GURU WARRIOR last start and she is probably only a place chance again. Others that shape as place chances are prolific winners YURI ROYALE (2) and MAGNETIC EDGE (4).
